4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to prepare them for a career in cybersecurity. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring 3 live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants per class. Students will acquire essential skills in Windows, Linux, and network administration, along with cloud security and penetration testing. The bootcamp emphasizes risk management strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop